		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Exalted Armor",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "reaction"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> a fiend attempts to Strike the exalted hunter and they're conscious of the attack</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> the exalted hunter's armor protects them against the fiend's Strike. The triggering creature must attempt at a @Check[will|dc:37] save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> the creature is unaffected and immune for 24h.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> The creature can attempt its attack and any other attacks against the target this turn.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature can't attack the target and wastes the action. It can't attempt further attacks against the target this turn.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature wastes the action and can't attempt to attack the target for the rest of sanctuary's duration.</p>",
